### Genfeed API - Hedra Integration Endpoints
### Manage Hedra AI video generation
### Handles: avatar videos, talking heads

########################################
# Video Generation
########################################

### Generate Talking Head Video
POST {{apiBaseUrl}}/integrations/hedra/generate
Authorization: Bearer {{bearerToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "imageId": "{{testImageId}}",
  "audioId": "{{testAudioId}}",
  "text": "Hello, this is a talking head video"
}


### Check Generation Status
GET {{apiBaseUrl}}/integrations/hedra/status/{{generationId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{bearerToken}}


########################################
# Test Cases
########################################

### Test: Invalid Generation ID
GET {{apiBaseUrl}}/integrations/hedra/status/invalid-id
Authorization: Bearer {{bearerToken}}


### Test: Unauthorized Access
POST {{apiBaseUrl}}/integrations/hedra/generate
